<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.10">
<l>aṅkav vāṉavark kākulam tīra vaṇiyi laṅkaiya ḻittavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>poṅku māvala vaṉkali kaṉṟi pukaṉṟa poṅkattaṅ  koṇṭuviv vulakil</l>
<l>eṅkum pāṭiniṉ ṟāṭumiṉ toṇṭī rimmai yēyiṭa rillaiyi ṟantāl</l>
<l>taṅku mūraṇṭa mēkaṇṭu koṇmiṉ cāṟṟi ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, dance and keep singing everywhere in this world</l>
<l rend="indent">with these “turbulent path” [songs]</l>
<l>Composed by Kalikaṉṟi, the one of abundant, great strength,</l>
<l rend="indent">about the one who destroyed beautiful Laṅkā,</l>
<l>To end the sorrows of the celestials there.</l>
<l rend="indent">In this life, there will be no sorrows</l>
<l>And, if you die, heaven will be the city where you abide. See for yourself.</l>
<l rend="indent">We declare, “Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
